OL,3,C'I just want people to remember how
OL,4,Cclose it is': says Ukrainian filmmaker
OL,6,FTwo thousand meters; it isn't very far.
OL,8,FA short stroll; no more than that.
OL,10,FBut in Ukraine, as film-maker Mstyslav
OL,11,FChernov tells me: "Every meter of land
OL,12,Fis someone's life and someone's
OL,13,Fblood.''
OL,15,FHis new documentary, 2000 Meters to
OL,16,FAndriivka, is raw reportage from the
OL,17,Ffront line of a single battle;
OL,18,Fharrowing, heart-breaking and often
OL,19,Fvery hard to watch.
