OL,3,C'I just want people to remember how
OL,4,Cclose it is': says Ukrainian filmmaker
OL,6,FThe fight is through a narrow strip of
OL,7,Fwoodland to recapture a village seized
OL,8,Fby the invading Russians.
OL,10,FChernov walked every step of the way
OL,11,Fwith Ukraine's Third Assault Brigade.
OL,12,FHe returned alive. Many more did not.
OL,14,F"My main goal was to keep the memory
OL,15,Fof those people - and to honour them
OL,16,Fand their names,'' he says. ''To
OL,17,Fexpress the strength of Ukrainian
OL,18,Fsoldiers who are protecting the land
OL,19,Fthat I call home.''
