OL,3,C'I just want people to remember how
OL,4,Cclose it is': says Ukrainian filmmaker
OL,6,FAlmost every soldier we meet along the
OL,7,Fway is ultimately doomed. There are no
OL,8,FHollywood heroes; just men, filled
OL,9,Fwith fear, doing their duty.
OL,11,FAnd yet Hollywood has already honoured
OL,12,FChernov for his previous film, 20 Days
OL,13,Fin Mariupol.
OL,15,FIn his Oscar's acceptance speech last
OL,16,Fyear, he said he would gladly swap the
OL,17,Faward for a Russian retreat from
OL,18,FUkraine.
