OL,3,C'I just want people to remember how
OL,4,Cclose it is': says Ukrainian filmmaker
OL,6,F"But if you turn on the Russian
OL,7,Ftelevision, they will keep saying that
OL,8,Fit takes only 20 minutes for a Russian
OL,9,Fnuclear bomb hit London, or it will
OL,10,Ftake only 24 hours for Russian tanks
OL,11,Fto reach Berlin.
OL,13,F"I just want people to remember how
OL,14,Fclose it is and how real it is."
