OL,3,C'I just want people to remember how
OL,4,Cclose it is': says Ukrainian filmmaker
OL,6,FIt is, he says a film, about distance
OL,7,Fand how deceptive that can be; the
OL,8,Flength of the woods becomes a chasm
OL,9,Fthe solders must bridge; the thousands
OL,10,Fof miles between the front line where
OL,11,Fso many sacrifice their lives and the
OL,12,Fpolitical leaders making the actual
OL,13,Fdecisions likely to decide Ukraine's
OL,14,Ffate.
OL,16,FAs we speak, America seems to be
OL,17,Flosing faith that Vladimir Putin will
OL,18,Fagree a ceasefire.
OL,20,FI ask him if he'd like to screen the
OL,21,Ffilm for President Trump.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
