OL,3,C'I just want people to remember how
OL,4,Cclose it is': says Ukrainian filmmaker
OL,6,F"I would love to screen this film for
OL,7,Fthe political establishment in US,''
OL,8,Fhe replies. "Just to pierce the
OL,9,Fbubble. The political bubble, abstract
OL,10,Fbubble, and just bring a little bit of
OL,11,Freality.
OL,13,F"There is so much false information
OL,14,Fthat reaches the ears of politicians
OL,15,Fwho are making big decisions. I'd love
OL,16,Fthem to see things how they really
OL,17,Fare.''
OL,19,F2000 Meters to Ardriivka brings the
OL,20,Fgrim reality far too close for
OL,21,Fcomfortable viewing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
