OL,3,C'I just want people to remember how
OL,4,Cclose it is': says Ukrainian filmmaker
OL,6,FIn the end, the soldiers achieve their
OL,7,Fobjective but it's a costly and
OL,8,Ffleeting victory. The Russians soon
OL,9,Freturn.
OL,11,FNo film, I have seen, captures so well
OL,12,Fthe futility of war ` nor, its
OL,13,Fabsolute necessity for those defending
OL,14,Ftheir homeland.
OL,16,F2000 Meters To Andriivka is in cinemas
OL,17,Ffrom Friday.
